data.title: Oando Annual Report 2012
data.meta_description: Oando Annual Report 2012 - Download as a PDF or view online for free
data.text: Oando PLC is an integrated energy company in sub-Saharan Africa engaged in upstream, midstream, and downstream operations. In 2012, it had total revenue of N673.2 billion with profit before tax of N17.6 billion and profit after tax of N10.8 billion. Key divisions include Oando Energy Resources (exploration and production), Oando Energy Services (energy services), and Oando Gas and Power (gas distribution and power solutions). Oando aims to become the leading indigenous energy company in Africa through continued investment and expansion across its operations.
